page.title: 19 PARISH NOTICES JULY 1985
page.content: The Falfield and Rockhampton News Sheet carried notification of the following events connected with the Church. Mondays - July 1st,15th,29th Whist Drives WI Notices - WI outing July 2nd. Sunday July 7th STRAWBERRY TEA in village hall. Tuesday 9th July WI meeting "Any Questions" Panel. Mothers' Union - Tuesday 16th July Quiet Day at Wickwar Church. Weds.17th July Fete meeting at cricket pavilion. Youth Club - Thursdays 4th,11th,18th and 25th July. Happy Circle - Afternoon tea at Mrs. Court's. Bingo - Fri 5th July in aid of village hall funds. Beetle Drive - Sat 13th July in V.Hall Grand Bingo in aid of Church and Cricket Club on cricket pitch Fri 26th July.
